-- Bahraini fund Mumtalakat to price benchmark-sized sukuk on Tues -leads
-- By David French
-- Mon Nov 17, 2014 04:40AM EST
-- None



DUBAI, Nov 17 (Reuters) - Bahrain sovereign fund Mumtalakat [BHMUT.UL] is aiming to price an Islamic bond issue of benchmark size and seven years duration on Tuesday, a document from lead arrangers said.

Price indications have yet to be confirmed, the document said on Monday. Benchmark size is typically understood to mean upwards of $500 million.